5
Vital Point to Capture?(10)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to play\b0 .
\par
\par White \'a1\'e2 stones are captured, but White can find a move which doesn't let Black to have a living shape.
\par
\par If you think about how would Black live if White plays elsewhere, it is easy to find the good move for White.
\par
\par
\par }
