Dia. 03 Illegal Move
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Against White \'a1\'e2, Black 1 is an excellent move.
\par
\par White plays at 2 and after Black's dansu at 3, it becomes a strange shape.
\par
\par White can't connect, because it would be an\cf1\b  illegal move\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par Therefore Black is alive.
\par
\par }
