Dia. 04 Living Move for Black
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Let's figure out how to live with Black, if White plays elsewhere.
\par
\par It is easy. If Black plays at 1 he can live. After that, if White takes with A, Black lives with the dansu at B.
\par
\par Therefore 1 is the vital point.
\par
\par \cf1\b Black can live if he plays at this place and White can capture Black if he plays here\cf0\b0 .
\par }
